Definition: Here we give a set of description and we can see how many different ways can we say in sentence to express the exact same thing.For example, I can say 'John is my father' or 'I'm John's son'. and these two sentences are actually talking about the same thing.

Negative Examples.input: Buzz Aldrin was born in Glen Ridge, New Jersey., Buzz Aldrin was born in Glen Ridge New Jersey., Buzz Aldrin's birth place was Glen Ridge, New Jersey.,
